5: Good day. We brought a delivery.
9:
Hello, Stella. I assume that's what I

11:

16:
Why are you carrying so many

21:

Yes, I'm interested in that

39:
Huh, guess there's a lot of people

43:
There are many accounts, yes... But

47:
It's possible some of them did, but

nobody in this world made a record

50:
Maybe a different kind of book will
give us a hint.
53:
But perhaps that's enough research

56:
We didn't really find much though.

The thing is, we actually received an

62:
It's too much for us to eat alone, so

73:
How's Subaru been doing lately? Is

77:
He's doing well. Yesterday, he came
home from a job full of energy and

79:

83:

86:

90:

99:

101:
Besides, Sister is far more

104:
I'm sorry for cutting the conversation

112:
No, no. I could never ask a guest to

117:
Hey, we've gone on adventures
together. You can consider us
friends, you know?
121:
I can help with everything but

126:
Understood. Then I'll gratefully

133:

142:
Thick blankets made out of feathers

151:
Your movements are very practiced.

155:
Oh, it's nothing fancy. Most of my

157:
Would you mind tasting the food for

165:
I won't lose to you in the kitchen. It's

172:
Thank you both for all the help. I was

175: I'm glad to be of assistance.
179:
Swing by Starview sometime with
the others. We'll treat you to dinner
and show you the sights.
189:
We're back!
Huh? What're you doing here, Alk?
192:
Just stopped by with a package
delivery. You guys must be tired and
hungry, right? Stella and I were just
about to leaveâ€”
196:
Hey, why don't you join us for
dinner? The more the merrier!
201:
That's a good idea. If you haven't
eaten yet, you should eat with us.
205: You sure? Well, thanks for having us.
213:
He inspired me to make a better
meal than usual.
217:
Whoa, seriously? I can't wait to see
how good everything tastes!
222:
Excuse you, Barusu. You should
already know that Rem's cooking is

234:
(It's kind of nice to spend our days

237:
(I don't know when we'll be able to
